# Documentation

This section covers documentation standards and the package checklist for the thunderstorm monorepo.

## Documentation Files

### [Process](./process.mdc)
Holistic package checklist for agents: understand the package, update `__package.json` and README, add documentation, copyright, license, tests, and ISSUES.md. Follow this when bringing a package to standard.

### [Standards](../documentation.mdc)
When and how to document code, what to document vs. what to skip, and documentation format guidelines. Lives at `package-standard/documentation.mdc`.

## Quick Reference

- **Bringing a package to standard?** → See [Process](./process.mdc) for the full checklist
- **Editing code?** → See [documentation.mdc](../documentation.mdc) for when to update docs
- **What to document?** → See [documentation.mdc](../documentation.mdc) for guidelines
